---
import Layout from '../layouts/RootLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="home" description="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet">

<section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
  
	<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Hello, stalker!</h1>


	<p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
    Welcome to Ilm (علم), a personal blogging software built on <a href="https://astro.build/" class="border-b border-current">Astro</a>.  
    This is a lightweight, text-first starting point for sharing thoughts, tutorials, and poems. Designed to be simple and fast,
	it focuses on content without unnecessary distractions. 
  </p>

  <!-- Quick links -->
  <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2 mb-8">
    <li><a href="/me" class="hover:underline">me (takes you to my portfolio)</a></li>
    <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:underline">blog posts</a></li>
    <li><a href="/projects" class="hover:underline">philosophy posts</a></li>
    <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:underline">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>


		<p class="mb-2">
		You can fully customize the post categories to suit your content.
		Just open <code>./src/consts.ts</code> and edit the category list or add your own.
		Want to rename a section like <code>/projects</code> or <code>/blog</code>? Go ahead — the structure is yours to shape.
		</p>
		<p class="pb-4 font-bold ">
			<i>This template is just a skeleton. Add, break, reshape. Make it yours.</i>
		</p>

  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
    This template comes with minimal styling.  
    Customize your header in <code>src/components/header.tsx</code> and footer in <code>src/components/footer.tsx</code>.
  </p>
</section>


</Layout>